description=Keeps your character alive and improving while AFK. Always-on survival autopilot — no setup needed. Handles hunger, thirst, sleep, exhaustion, wounds (auto-bandage), and boredom automatically. Exercises to level Strength and Fitness using the best available equipment. Fights zombies when cornered; flees when bleeding or outnumbered. Bulk-loots nearby buildings, tracks depleted containers, and expands radius when supplies run low. Splitscreen supported — keyboard player uses F10; controller players use Back/Select double-tap. Client-side only — no server mod required.
